Data needing to be passed to keep players up to date with a game:
- Game Type: i.e. Snap, etc.
- No Players
- Current Game State:
  - Player hands
  - Central Stack
  - Game state enum
  - Last Action
  - Player's turn
  - Timestamp



e.g.

{
  type: "snap",
  players: [
    {
      playerNo: 1,
      currentHand: [
        {
          suit: "hearts",
          value: "3"
        },
        {
          suit: "clubs",
          value: "king"
        }, etc.
      ]
    }
  ],
  lastAction: {
    playerNo: 2,
    action: {
      type: "callSnap",
      result: "failure"
    }
  }
}